WEBVTT

00:02.877 --> 00:06.172
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:06.256 --> 00:09.217
<i>[music intensifies]</i>

00:09.300 --> 00:16.391
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:27.777 --> 00:30.071
[people yelling, screaming]

00:58.725 --> 00:59.851
- Dri!

00:59.934 --> 01:01.394
- What's going on?

01:01.478 --> 01:03.188
- We need to go.

01:09.694 --> 01:12.155
- [grunting]

01:21.748 --> 01:24.334
- [panting]

01:24.417 --> 01:25.585
- Oh, my God!

01:25.668 --> 01:28.129
- What's happening?
[both whimpering]

01:35.720 --> 01:39.390
[people screaming]

01:39.474 --> 01:42.769
- [panting]

01:42.852 --> 01:44.437
- No, no, no!

01:48.066 --> 01:50.568
[shimmering tone]

01:51.820 --> 01:53.613
- Why do you have a Union card?

01:53.696 --> 01:55.573
- There's a lot
you don't understand.

01:55.657 --> 01:57.951
[jet engines whirring]

02:02.247 --> 02:04.624
- Chase is...fighting them.

02:04.707 --> 02:06.793
[crash]

02:12.841 --> 02:14.843
Aah!

02:17.595 --> 02:18.972
[both panting]

02:19.055 --> 02:20.807
We'll be safe in here!

02:23.726 --> 02:26.729
<i>[energetic electronic music]</i>

02:26.813 --> 02:33.903
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:31.252 --> 03:34.172
[indistinct chatter]

03:34.255 --> 03:36.215
[children shouting]

03:41.471 --> 03:43.222
[laughter]

03:43.306 --> 03:47.477
- Through Ascension, you join
our ancestors in the Flow.

03:47.560 --> 03:52.190
All become one,
in the true community.

03:55.610 --> 03:57.612
- You're all fucking insane!
[people gasp]

03:57.695 --> 03:59.322
- Shh!

04:07.080 --> 04:08.665
- I can't spend
any more Sundays

04:08.748 --> 04:10.667
watching people
kill themselves!

04:22.553 --> 04:26.140
- Baby, if you just give
the Omnifaith a chance--

04:26.224 --> 04:29.268
- The Union's responsible
for killing my brother!

04:29.352 --> 04:31.312
Your son!

04:32.438 --> 04:34.565
- Whether or not you share
my beliefs,

04:34.649 --> 04:36.859
my job is to protect you.

04:36.943 --> 04:39.404
- I'm done listening.

04:40.989 --> 04:44.117
- [crying]

04:45.285 --> 04:47.537
Merciful inhabitants
of the Flow.

04:47.620 --> 04:50.123
You who are together,
my ancestors

04:50.206 --> 04:52.792
and my enemies as one,

04:52.875 --> 04:56.879
please protect the only child
I have left.

05:05.638 --> 05:07.724
<i>- [gasps]</i>

05:07.807 --> 05:10.226
- Juju. Mama's here.

05:11.436 --> 05:13.438
<i>- Ma? You're alive!</i>

05:18.776 --> 05:21.154
<i>Am I...dead?</i>

05:21.821 --> 05:25.533
- No, baby, you're alive.
We're alive.

05:27.285 --> 05:29.203
<i>- What's happening to me?</i>

05:31.539 --> 05:34.876
- You are saved, child.

05:43.593 --> 05:47.096
<i>We 12 never knew each other,</i>

05:47.180 --> 05:50.349
<i>but we had two points</i>
<i>of commonality:</i>

05:50.433 --> 05:53.728
<i>we were all atheists,</i>
<i>and scientists,</i>

05:53.811 --> 05:56.606
<i>working to harness</i>
<i>nano-technology</i>

05:56.689 --> 06:01.152
to stop the climate collapse
that races toward us still.

06:02.111 --> 06:04.072
- The Flow is powered
by the Kaaba!

06:04.155 --> 06:06.657
You really think heaven
would need a battery?

06:06.741 --> 06:08.117
Wake up!

06:09.786 --> 06:14.957
- Then, our own nano-technology
consumed us.

06:15.041 --> 06:18.795
I woke up in the HereAfter.
A miracle!

06:18.878 --> 06:20.254
- Ugh.

06:20.338 --> 06:24.383
I've heard this boring story
a million times.

06:24.467 --> 06:26.511
- And you will hear it
a million more

06:26.594 --> 06:29.388
until you accept the truth.
[person shushing]

06:29.472 --> 06:31.140
- Naked before the Kaaba,

06:31.224 --> 06:35.311
surrounded by relics
of the Old Religions,

06:35.394 --> 06:37.688
<i>fate's message was clear:</i>

06:37.772 --> 06:40.316
<i>to survive the death</i>
<i>of our ecosystem,</i>

06:40.399 --> 06:43.653
<i>we must bring</i>
<i>all faiths together.</i>

06:43.736 --> 06:46.280
<i>And so we built Babylon.</i>

06:46.364 --> 06:50.368
<i>Here, we prepare</i>
<i>for the Twilight:</i>

06:50.451 --> 06:56.499
that glorious day when all
have accepted the Omnifaith,

06:56.582 --> 06:59.919
and the last man Ascends.

07:00.002 --> 07:04.090
That day, the Nano-Euphrates
will run gold

07:04.173 --> 07:06.092
as the rays of the sun,

07:06.175 --> 07:11.180
to signify humanity
has finally beaten death.

07:13.057 --> 07:14.892
The sun has set.

07:14.976 --> 07:19.355
May those who have earned
Ascension step forward.

07:20.940 --> 07:26.362
Through this rite, you join
our ancestors in the Flow.

07:26.445 --> 07:31.534
You become one
in the true community.

07:48.759 --> 07:50.720
- Juju? Baby?

07:52.555 --> 07:54.348
<i>- You know, I used</i>
<i>to be embarrassed</i>

07:54.432 --> 07:55.641
<i>when you called me that.</i>

07:55.725 --> 07:57.018
<i>But I gotta admit,</i>

07:57.101 --> 08:00.062
<i>it sounds good right</i>
<i>about now.</i>

08:01.230 --> 08:02.690
<i>Ma, where are we?</i>

08:02.773 --> 08:05.818
<i>Last I remember,</i>
<i>the Union slashed my eye.</i>

08:05.902 --> 08:09.780
<i>I thought I was dead,</i>
<i>but I'm still in gen:LOCK.</i>

08:09.864 --> 08:11.741
- The Union saved you.

08:13.117 --> 08:14.952
<i>- Ma, the Union</i>
<i>aren't good guys!</i>

08:15.036 --> 08:17.371
<i>They're zealots marching to</i>
<i>their deaths for fairy tales.</i>

08:17.455 --> 08:19.749
- The Miracle is not
a fairy tale.

08:19.832 --> 08:21.417
You don't understand.

08:21.500 --> 08:24.670
The Flow used Brother Tate
to answer my prayers.

08:24.754 --> 08:28.758
I prayed for a reunion
with my children every night.

08:28.841 --> 08:31.427
<i>- Children? Who else is there?</i>

08:31.511 --> 08:35.514
- Baby? What can I do?

08:39.185 --> 08:41.687
- In our attempt to free Chase
from the Polity,

08:41.771 --> 08:44.232
he was badly damaged.

08:44.315 --> 08:46.067
I'm so sorry, sister.

08:46.150 --> 08:49.946
We did not know
he would be so broken.

08:50.029 --> 08:51.489
- Pain that only gets worse.

08:51.572 --> 08:54.575
Memories vanishing,
he doesn't have a body.

08:54.659 --> 08:57.161
What kind of life is that?

08:57.245 --> 08:59.205
- No kind of life at all.

09:00.665 --> 09:02.041
But I've been thinking

09:02.124 --> 09:04.377
maybe there is a way
for his suffering

09:04.460 --> 09:07.046
and yours
to have been worth it.

09:10.216 --> 09:11.634
<i>- You want to Ascend?</i>

09:11.717 --> 09:13.469
You have no proof
of an afterlife

09:13.552 --> 09:14.804
in the Flow, Baba!

09:14.887 --> 09:17.348
- The testimonies of
the Saint Scientists

09:17.431 --> 09:20.351
are proof enough
for a billion people.

09:20.434 --> 09:24.146
[coughing]

09:24.230 --> 09:27.900
- Yasamin, your father is sick.
He is in great pain.

09:27.984 --> 09:31.320
Ascension will free him.

09:31.404 --> 09:33.531
And I want to go with him.

09:33.614 --> 09:37.076
- [gasps] But you aren't sick!

09:37.159 --> 09:38.828
- You don't need us.
- [wheezing]

09:38.911 --> 09:40.705
- You're an adult now, Yasamin.

09:40.788 --> 09:42.873
- Do you not see, daughter?

09:42.957 --> 09:46.085
We cannot Ascend
while you are without faith.

09:46.168 --> 09:48.004
[coughing]

09:48.087 --> 09:49.547
- But--
- No, buts!

09:49.630 --> 09:51.632
Your disbelief
is the only reason

09:51.716 --> 09:53.259
your father lives in pain.

10:03.269 --> 10:07.356
<i>- These sheep just</i>
<i>"go with the Flow."</i>

10:07.440 --> 10:09.525
<i>[crowd cheers]</i>
<i>[laughing]</i>

10:09.608 --> 10:11.402
<i>And I, Meshach,</i>

10:11.485 --> 10:15.197
<i>will wake them up.</i>
<i>[laughs]</i>

10:15.281 --> 10:19.035
<i>crowd: Meshach, Meshach--</i>
[broadcast powers off]

10:19.118 --> 10:22.330
<i>[solemn music]</i>

10:22.413 --> 10:29.503
<i>♪ ♪</i>

10:39.972 --> 10:43.434
- Juju, do you remember
your father?

10:43.517 --> 10:44.977
<i>- Only in flashes.</i>

10:45.061 --> 10:48.856
<i>I feel...empty</i>
<i>where he's supposed to be.</i>

10:50.983 --> 10:52.693
<i>- Your father and I</i>
<i>were children</i>

10:52.777 --> 10:55.738
<i>when the United Nations</i>
<i>rebranded as the Polity.</i>

10:55.821 --> 10:58.491
<i>They changed their name,</i>
<i>but the old hierarchies</i>

10:58.574 --> 10:59.909
<i>didn't go away.</i>

10:59.992 --> 11:02.411
<i>Mother Earth still got sicker.</i>

11:02.495 --> 11:04.413
<i>The poor, poorer.</i>

11:04.497 --> 11:06.165
<i>To me, it was a farce.</i>

11:06.248 --> 11:09.085
<i>But your father believed</i>
<i>in making change from within.</i>

11:09.168 --> 11:13.214
<i>He had so much optimism.</i>
<i>It radiated into me.</i>

11:13.297 --> 11:15.216
<i>Until he passed away.</i>

11:15.299 --> 11:18.260
<i>When I didn't have his faith</i>
<i>in the Polity around,</i>

11:18.344 --> 11:21.639
<i>I found once again</i>
<i>that I had none of my own.</i>

11:21.722 --> 11:25.476
<i>So I became the "traitor"</i>
<i>you now see before you.</i>

11:28.187 --> 11:31.899
<i>- Mom, I'm scared.</i>
<i>Was Dad ever scared?</i>

11:37.196 --> 11:40.825
- Of course,
but he put on a brave face.

11:41.700 --> 11:44.412
<i>- That's...good to know.</i>

11:50.292 --> 11:53.337
- Terrorists destroyed
these monuments long ago.

11:53.421 --> 11:55.464
The Flow rebuilt them,

11:55.548 --> 11:58.342
only for the Polity
to destroy them again.

11:58.426 --> 12:01.846
- And foolish the Polity
was to destroy them.

12:01.929 --> 12:03.305
Hello, Julian.

12:03.389 --> 12:06.642
<i>- [groaning]</i>
<i>I can't live like this, Ma!</i>

12:06.725 --> 12:08.894
- Thankfully,
you do not have to.

12:08.978 --> 12:12.690
- What? I--
- Hush now. And listen.

12:12.773 --> 12:14.358
Years before the Miracle,

12:14.442 --> 12:16.277
I was a young man
living in Australia,

12:16.360 --> 12:19.321
when fire ate
the continent entire.

12:19.405 --> 12:23.409
I lost everyone. My wife.
My children.

12:23.492 --> 12:27.329
But that suffering,
that unreal suffering,

12:27.413 --> 12:29.999
I believe,
is why fate chose me.

12:30.082 --> 12:34.044
<i>- It's not just the pain.</i>
<i>It's the fear.</i>

12:34.128 --> 12:37.006
<i>I can see</i>
<i>the dark places in me.</i>

12:37.089 --> 12:41.177
<i>It's like</i>
<i>I'm watching myself...vanish.</i>

12:41.260 --> 12:45.347
- Julian, there are many ways
one can earn their Ascension.

12:45.431 --> 12:47.475
But by far the hardest way

12:47.558 --> 12:51.353
to earn Ascension
is through suffering.

12:52.188 --> 12:54.482
None have earned
their Ascension

12:54.565 --> 12:57.985
through suffering
more truly than you.

12:58.068 --> 13:00.488
- The Union has the technology
to make you

13:00.571 --> 13:02.698
Ascend the way you are,

13:02.781 --> 13:06.702
to build a temporary biological
body for the transfer.

13:06.785 --> 13:09.830
You can be free of pain,
in heaven.

13:11.040 --> 13:12.875
<i>- I'm scared to Ascend.</i>

13:12.958 --> 13:18.214
<i>I've died twice,</i>
<i>and it was...terrible.</i>

13:18.297 --> 13:20.090
- Which is why
I'm gonna show you

13:20.174 --> 13:26.472
that Ascension is not death,
but glorious eternal life.

13:26.555 --> 13:29.600
<i>[somber organ music]</i>

13:29.683 --> 13:34.021
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:34.104 --> 13:38.484
- Through Ascension,
you join our ancestors.

13:38.567 --> 13:42.488
You become one
in the true community.

13:45.658 --> 13:47.910
- Come here, baby.

13:47.993 --> 13:49.537
Don't worry.

13:49.620 --> 13:53.415
When you're ready, I'll be here
in the river of us all,

13:53.499 --> 13:55.751
waiting for you.

14:16.981 --> 14:18.857
<i>- I'm ready.</i>

14:20.526 --> 14:22.528
<i>I'm ready to join her.</i>

14:22.611 --> 14:25.155
- I'll have your transfer body
ready tomorrow.

14:25.239 --> 14:28.617
I am honored to shepherd
you through this.

14:41.755 --> 14:43.841
- Six weeks you haven't been
to a meeting.

14:43.924 --> 14:47.011
Now you want us to bomb
the freaking Kaaba?

14:47.094 --> 14:49.471
- The only time we can
go unseen is night,

14:49.555 --> 14:51.432
but then the Flow runs dark.

14:51.515 --> 14:53.809
It won't let us
get anywhere near.

14:54.768 --> 14:57.771
- Ah, but the holy boats
are immune!

15:10.743 --> 15:12.494
Narong, stop eating the grain

15:12.578 --> 15:14.705
that keeps the bombs
from shifting around.

15:14.788 --> 15:17.583
- Even prisoners get
a last meal!

15:17.666 --> 15:19.501
[boom]

15:32.014 --> 15:35.517
- [gasps]
That's a Polity Plane.

15:39.271 --> 15:42.775
[people screaming]

15:49.281 --> 15:53.369
[electric crackling]

16:10.886 --> 16:14.056
[booming]

16:17.393 --> 16:20.020
[power down hum]

16:23.732 --> 16:26.527
<i>[tense music]</i>

16:26.610 --> 16:31.073
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:31.156 --> 16:32.991
- Oof--

16:48.507 --> 16:50.008
Ohh...

16:50.092 --> 16:51.552
Aah!

17:01.145 --> 17:02.563
<i>- Mission successful.</i>

17:02.646 --> 17:05.023
<i>Union nano energy source,</i>
<i>eliminated.</i>

17:05.107 --> 17:07.359
<i>Civilian death toll</i>
<i>stands at--</i>

17:10.320 --> 17:13.115
- All their talk of peace
while producing something

17:13.198 --> 17:15.325
as dangerous as nanotech,

17:15.409 --> 17:18.579
refusing to allow
our inspectors in.

17:18.662 --> 17:21.707
We couldn't let the Polity
live under that threat.

17:32.509 --> 17:35.554
- Our after-life is gone.

17:50.235 --> 17:51.570
- Oh.

17:51.653 --> 17:56.074
Oh, ye of little faith.
[both cry]

18:01.246 --> 18:04.666
The short notice with which
you called this meeting

18:04.750 --> 18:08.879
is a disrespect.
You are not my superior.

18:08.962 --> 18:12.925
I am the only one among us with
a military background and--

18:13.008 --> 18:15.636
<i>- Your military background</i>
<i>is a black stain,</i>

18:15.719 --> 18:17.846
<i>not a bragging right.</i>

18:17.930 --> 18:20.516
<i>The 11 of us are Athenians,</i>

18:20.599 --> 18:23.602
<i>while you remain</i>
<i>ever the Spartan.</i>

18:31.485 --> 18:32.694
<i>[automatic gunfire]</i>

18:32.778 --> 18:35.572
- They have a copy of Julian?

18:36.740 --> 18:39.952
<i>- And the new gen:LOCK</i>
<i>recruits besides.</i>

18:40.035 --> 18:42.538
<i>With the ability</i>
<i>to copy souls,</i>

18:42.621 --> 18:45.040
<i>the Polity will</i>
<i>no longer be limited</i>

18:45.123 --> 18:48.585
<i>to the rare plastic mind</i>
<i>they happen across.</i>

18:48.669 --> 18:51.296
<i>Now they can just copy</i>
<i>the ones they have,</i>

18:51.380 --> 18:54.049
<i>make infinite Holons.</i>

18:54.132 --> 18:58.220
<i>They will surely build an army</i>
<i>of these bodiless souls.</i>

18:58.303 --> 19:01.056
- To stop the salvation
we bring.

19:01.139 --> 19:02.140
I'll do what I must.

19:02.224 --> 19:05.853
<i>- As must we all, together.</i>

19:07.020 --> 19:11.817
citizens: Together!
Together! Together! Together!

19:11.900 --> 19:15.028
[chanting continues]

19:15.112 --> 19:17.614
- [laughing in amazement]

19:17.698 --> 19:21.368
- [gasps] How can it be?

19:24.663 --> 19:27.332
[indistinct chatter]

19:39.261 --> 19:41.346
- Close that,
you'll get us caught.

19:41.430 --> 19:42.973
- I'm gathering intel!

19:43.056 --> 19:46.351
<i>- Despite the destruction</i>
<i>of our great Kaaba,</i>

19:46.435 --> 19:48.812
<i>the Flow carries on.</i>

19:48.896 --> 19:51.690
- What? But that's impossible!

19:51.773 --> 19:55.277
<i>- The Flow no longer</i>
<i>requires the Kaaba.</i>

19:55.360 --> 19:58.906
<i>It has the capacity</i>
<i>to self-perpetuate,</i>

19:58.989 --> 20:02.910
<i>A second Miracle!</i>
<i>But no longer can we let those</i>

20:02.993 --> 20:06.663
<i>who trespassed against us</i>
<i>go unpunished.</i>

20:06.747 --> 20:07.706
[cheers and applause]

20:07.789 --> 20:09.291
<i>The Polity attacked.</i>

20:09.374 --> 20:13.462
<i>They attempted</i>
<i>to destroy Heaven itself.</i>

20:13.545 --> 20:15.964
[crowd booing]
<i>They just started a war.</i>

20:16.048 --> 20:18.425
<i>We will end it.</i>
[cheers and applause]

20:18.508 --> 20:20.552
<i>And we've already begun.</i>

20:20.636 --> 20:24.765
<i>Our drones caught footage</i>
<i>of Union terrorists</i>

20:24.848 --> 20:28.060
<i>aiding the Polity</i>
<i>in their attack!</i>

20:28.143 --> 20:32.064
<i>We are dealing with them...</i>
<i>now.</i>

20:32.147 --> 20:35.192
<i>And Ascensions continue!</i>

20:35.275 --> 20:39.738
<i>When our great intellectuals,</i>
<i>Minu and Farzin,</i>

20:39.821 --> 20:44.326
<i>found out their daughter</i>
<i>was not only a disbeliever,</i>

20:44.409 --> 20:48.455
<i>but attempted to doom</i>
<i>all humanity.</i>

21:05.973 --> 21:07.182
- [screaming]

21:07.265 --> 21:10.560
<i>[intense music]</i>

21:10.644 --> 21:14.272
<i>♪ ♪</i>

21:14.356 --> 21:17.317
[crowd jeering]

21:27.619 --> 21:28.954
- We can't stay here.

21:29.037 --> 21:31.665
We'll be safe in the Euphrates
until night.

21:32.708 --> 21:35.627
- Night has already
fallen for me.

21:54.312 --> 21:57.190
- Bless me, Sister,
for I have sinned.

21:58.233 --> 22:01.069
When the Polity
struck the Kaaba, the 12,

22:01.153 --> 22:02.571
we knew the Flow had long

22:02.654 --> 22:05.741
before ceased needing
an external power source.

22:05.824 --> 22:10.037
We only kept it secret
so the Polity would not know.

22:10.120 --> 22:12.622
Now our enemy
possesses the means

22:12.706 --> 22:17.044
to build an army of Holons
impervious to our nano-tech.

22:17.127 --> 22:20.672
And if we are to stand a chance
against that army,

22:20.756 --> 22:22.966
I must break a promise to a boy

22:23.050 --> 22:25.886
to free him
from his great pain.

22:25.969 --> 22:29.014
<i>- [chuckles]</i>
<i>Correct me if I am wrong,</i>

22:29.097 --> 22:31.558
<i>but are not Spartans</i>
<i>remembered largely</i>

22:31.641 --> 22:34.102
<i>on account</i>
<i>of their great strength?</i>

22:47.532 --> 22:50.410
<i>- Thank you for helping me</i>
<i>Ascend, Brother.</i>

22:50.494 --> 22:54.122
<i>Since I woke up, I've seen</i>
<i>so much kindness in the Union.</i>

22:54.206 --> 22:56.458
<i>But none greater than yours.</i>

22:57.459 --> 22:58.835
- To take this journey,

22:58.919 --> 23:02.422
you'll have to go
into a body one last time.

23:14.976 --> 23:16.520
<i>- I'm coming, Ma.</i>

23:26.488 --> 23:30.367
[electricity crackling]

23:33.036 --> 23:34.246
What's going on?

23:38.458 --> 23:40.502
- I'm so sorry, Chase.

23:40.585 --> 23:44.506
But my duty is to all
the children of the Union.

23:44.589 --> 23:48.009
The Polity will build an army
using your soul,

23:48.093 --> 23:53.014
and damn mankind to death
without the HereAfter.

23:54.933 --> 23:59.354
Every faith had one like you
chosen to suffer in winter,

23:59.437 --> 24:01.857
to bring forth spring.

24:02.649 --> 24:06.736
But through suffering,
you will earn your Ascension.

24:06.820 --> 24:10.198
Like a golem,
you will protect us.

24:18.373 --> 24:20.667
- [yelling]

24:22.043 --> 24:24.671
Kill the copy.

24:24.754 --> 24:28.008
<i>[ominous music]</i>

24:28.091 --> 24:31.094
<i>♪ ♪</i>
